---
// RefreshToast.astro
// Appears 10s after iframe loads — prompts user to refresh if content is blank
---

<div
  id="refresh-toast"
  class="fixed bottom-5 right-5 bg-atlantis-900 text-white py-3 px-5 rounded-lg shadow-lg opacity-0 transition-opacity duration-300 z-50 hidden"
>
  <p>
    Tampilan kosong?
    <a href="#" id="refresh-toast-link" class="underline hover:text-atlantis-300">
      Refresh
    </a>
  </p>
</div>
